tafsir[55]{c,v,t}:
  54,1,"Darngal ngal hewtii, lewru ndun kadi seekinoke gila fewndo Annabiijo (jom kisiyee on). Seekagol ndu ngol woni maande laa…ďunde."
  54,2,"Si sirkoo…ďe …ďen yi'ii maande e hujja goongin…óo Nulaa…óo on (yo o his), …ďe …óuurnoo ja…ďugol …óum, …ďe wi'a: …óii hujjaaji e …ďannganduyeeji …ói men yi'i, ko mbilewu meerente."
  54,3,"∆Āe fenni goonga ka o addani …ďe kan, …ďe jokki mbelee…óe ma…ď…ďe fennugol ngol. Hara le fiyaaku kala - mo∆ī∆īi maa boni - ko wa…óay…óum no haaniri non √Ďalande Darngal."
  54,4,"Gom…óii kumpite mofte …óe Alllah halkirnoo yeddugol too√Īa arii e ma…ď…ďe, yeru ko …ďe ha…óitora yeddugol too√Īa."
  54,5,"Kon ko ari e ma…ď…ďe, ko √Īe√Ī∆īal timmungal, fii no wonira hujja e ma…ď…ďe. Kono jertingol nafataa yim…ďe …ďe gom…óintaa Allah e √Ďalaande sakkitiinde."
  54,6,"Si …ďe salanike ma an Nulaa…óo, selu …ďe …óuurno…óaa …ďe, habbito…óaa √Īalnde noddoowo halfinaa…óo wuttoygol ngol ka allaandu noddoyta e huunde a√Īiniinde, nde tawata tageefo anndaano sugu mayre ko adii."
  54,7,"Jaasu…ďe e ndaar…óe, hi…ďe yaltira e genaale …óen faade ka √Īaawirde, wano kanuuji carotoo…ói, hakkee hawjere."
  54,8,"He√Īanii…ďe noddoowo on ka √Īaawirde. Heefer…ďe …ďen wi'a: ndee …óoo ko √Īalaande sattunde. Tawde hinde wonnde e ca…óeele e kulhuli."
  54,9,"Ado …ďee yeddu…ďe ma …óoo an Nulaa…óo, hari yim…ďe Nuuhu …ďen yeddiino. ∆Āe fenni ko Men nuli kon jeyaa…óo Amen on Nuuhu e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe wi'i woo: ko jinnaa…óo ! …ďe purii mo noone fow wiide si o accaali noddugol …ďe."
  54,10,"O torii Joomi makko, wonnde : yim…ďe am …ďen foolii lam, …ďe ja…ďanaali lam. Faaboram jippinirgol leopte e dow ma…ď…ďe."
  54,11,"Men udditiri dammbu…óe kammu ngun, ndiyam saa∆īay…óam jokkondira."
  54,12,"Men tu…ď…ďiniri leydi ndin …ďulli ndiyam. Ndiyam …óam ka kammu e …óam ka leydi fottiri yamiroore Allah hoddiranoonde ko …ďooyi. ∆äam yooli fow, si wanna …ďe Allah da…ónunoo …ďe."
  54,13,"Men roondorii Nuuhu e laana lesaaka marka alluwe e peŇče. Men da…óndi mo kanko e wondunoo…ďe e ma…ď…ďe …ďen yoolagol."
  54,14,"Ka laana no dogira e mororonje maayo e ngon, ndenka Amen. ∆äum ko faabo Nuuhu ngon non e ko yim…ďe makko …ďen fenni mo kon, …ďe yeddi ko o addani …ďe kon immorde ka Allah."
  54,15,"Gom…óii Men fillitorii kon ko Men leptirnoo …ďe, waaju e tasakuyee. Taw non si woodi waajitry…óo …óum?"
  54,16,"Taskii ko honno lepte Am …óen wa'unoo? E ko honno jertinol Am halkugol …ďe ngol wa'unoo?"
  54,17,"Gom…óii Men newinirii Alquur'aanaare nden waajitorgol. Hara no woodi waajitoray…óo tasakuyeeji mayre."
  54,18,"Aadi'en fennuno Annabaajo ma…ď…ďe on Huudu. Onon yim…ďe Makka, teskee ko honno lepte Am …óen wa'unoo e ma…ď…ďe? Tasko…óon kadi ko honno Mi jertinirnoo …óe wo…ó…ďe goo?"
  54,19,"Men wurtu e ma…ď…ďe henndu tii…óundu …ďuu…ďol, e √Īalaande …ďaleere, duumodaynde e ma…ď…ďe haa ka Jahiimi."
  54,20,"Hindu wippitira yim…ďe …ďen e leydi ndin, ndu bugora …ďe ko'e ma…ď…ďe …óen, wa si tawii ko …ďe da∆ī∆īe …óoofaade e jayru."
  54,21,"Taskee onon yim…ďe Makka …ďen, ko honno lepte Am …óen wa'unoo e ma…ď…ďe? Tasko…óon kadi ko honno Mi jertinirnoo …óe wo…ó…ďe goo?"
  54,22,"Gom…óii Men newinirii Alquur'aanaare nden waajitorgol. Hara no woodi waajitoray…óo tasakuyeeji mayre."
  54,23,"Samuuda'en fennuno waaju Nulaa…óo ma…ď…ďe on Saalih (yo o his)."
  54,24,"∆Āe wi'i hi…ďe yedda : kere ko ne…ó…óo gooto e amen woni ko men jokkata? Si men wa…óii …óum, haray ontuma men wonii woopu…ďe sari'a oo√Īiini e mun, woni kadi e tampere."
  54,25,"Hara ko e makko wahayu on jippinaa hakkunde amen? O heertora …óum hakkunde amen? Si ko woni, ko fenoowo nii, townitii…óo."
  54,26,"Aray …ďe annda √Ďalnde Janngo, ko hommbo woni fenoowo townitii…óo on? Anndon si Saalih kaa ko kam…ďe?"
  54,27,"Ko Men yaltiniroo…ďe ngelooba ndewa mbam ka fetere, Men wurtira mba e ma…ď…ďe, jarribagol …ďe. Aynitu…ďe …ďe an Saalih, tinaa ko …ďe wa…óata mba e ko …ďe huuwetee ontuma, mu√Ī√Īo…óaa lorra ma…ď…ďe."
  54,28,"Humitu…ďe wonnde ndiyam woyndu ma…ď…ďe ndun, ko senndaa…óam hakkunde e ma…ď…ďe e ngelooba mbam: mba yara √Īallal, …ďe yara √Īallal. Kala ma…ď…ďe yara ge…ďal mun ka√Īum tun, e √Īalaande mun nden."
  54,29,"∆Āe noddiri wonndii…óo ma…ď…ďe on, fii warugol mba. O jonni kaafa kan, o wari mba e yamaruyee yim…ďe makko …ďen."
  54,30,"Taskee onon yim…ďe Makka …ďen, ko honno lepte Am …óen wa'unoo e ma…ď…ďe? Tasko…óon kadi ko honno Mi jertinirnoo …óum e wo…ó…ďe goo?"
  54,31,"Ko haacaango wooturu tun Men wurtunoo e ma…ď…ďe, ngo halki …ďe, …ďe wa'i le…ó…óe caŇče yooru…óe …óe gaynaako wallitorta dammi mun."
  54,32,"Gom…óii Men newinirii Alquur'aanaare nden waajitorgol. Hara no woodi waajitoray…óo tasakuyeeji mayre."
  54,33,"Yum…ďe Luutu …ďen fennuno waaju Nulaa…óo ma…ď…ďe on Luutu (yo o his)."
  54,34,"Men wurtuno henndu kaa∆īe e ma…ď…ďe, si wanaa e …ďeynguure Luutu nden (yo o his) lepte …óen hewtaano …ďe, tawde Men da…ónuno …ďe fewndo o yaltidunoo e ma…ď…ďe ka wenndoogo, ado lepte …óen yanude e …ďeya."
  54,35,"Men da…óniri …ďe lepte …óen, mo∆ī∆īere Amen e ma…ď…ďe. Ko wano Men yo…ďitiri non Luutu, Men yo…ďitirta kala yettu…óo neema Allah on e makko."
  54,36,"Gom…óii le Luutu hul…ďinirno …ďe lepte Amen …óen. Kono …ďe yeddondiri e jertinol makko gol, …ďe fenni mo."
  54,37,"Gom…óii …ďe …óa…ď…ďirno Luutu accidugol …ďe e ho…ó…ďe makko …ďen, fii no …ďe huuwira paŇčnkare e ma…ď…ďe. Laatii Men mahi gite ma…ď…ďe …óen, …ďe acci yi'ude, …ďe wi'ani …ďe: mee…óee non lepte …óen e bone salagol jertinol Am ngol."
  54,38,"Gom…óii lepte duumii…óe dawiranno …ďe bimmbi law, ko heddoda e ma…ď…ďe haa laakara, lepte …óen ton kadi he…ďa …ďe."
  54,39,"∆Āe wi'aee ontuma: Mee…óee lepte Am …óe Mi li…ďi e mon …óen, e salagol mon jertiaango Luutu ngol."
  54,40,"Gom…óii Men newinirii Alquur'aanaare nden waajitorgol. Hara no woodi waajitoray…óo tesakuyeeji mayre."
  54,41,"Gom…óii jertinaango Amen ngon arii e yim…ďe Fir'awna …ďen, e dow …óemngal Muusaa e Haaruuna, yo …ďe his."
  54,42,"∆Āe fenni kala hujja e …ďanngannduyeeji immor…ói e Amen. Men yagginiri …ďe fennugol …ďe ngol, lepte Foolu…óo Mo fooletaake, Hattan…óo Mo ronkataa hay huunde."
  54,43,"Kere ko heefer…ďe mon …ďen onon yim…ďe Makkah …ďen, …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e dii …ďeya heefer…ďe jantaa…ďe (Yim…ďe Nuuhu, e Aadi'en, e Samuuda'en, e Yim…ďe Luutu …ďen e Fir'awna e yim…ďe mun?) Kaa ko da…óugol e lepte Allah …óen woni maandinanaa on e Defte jippii…óe …óen?"
  54,44,"Kaa hara …ďee heefer…ďe Maakkah wi'ay: menen ko men dental wallindiroo…ďe e hoore kala faandanii…óo men bone, e…ď…ďu…óo senndugol men?"
  54,45,"Aray nden dental …ďee heefer…ďe foolee, …ďe huccintina …ďabbe, yeeso gom…óim…ďe …ďen. ∆äum wa…óuno √Īalnde hare nde Badri."
  54,46,"Wurin ko Darngal ngal …ďe fennunoo ngal, woni fodoore leptugol …ďe ngol. Ko Darngal non …ďuri mawnude e sa…ótude lepte dii ko …ďe leptanoo kon aduna ka Badri."
  54,47,"pellet, bonnir…ďe geddi e keeferaaku …ďen, wonii e majjere wo…ó…óiinde goonga, e lepte e tampere kadi."
  54,48,"√Ďalnde …ďe daasiroytee geece ma…ď…ďe …óen ka nder Yiite, …ďe wi'anee : mee…óee non lepte Yiite ngen."
  54,49,"Men tagir huunde kala e e…ď…ďoore Amen yawtunde, tippude e anndal e muy…óe Amen, wonndude e ko Men winndunoo ka Alluwal reenaangal."
  54,50,"Si Men faandanike huunde, yamiroore Amen e mayre wonataa, si wanaa konngol gootol pet, woni wiide : laato, nde laatora no Men faaliraa, yaawira wa hin∆īaango yiitere."
  54,51,"Gom…óii Men halkiino goree…ďe mon heefer…ďe mofte adinoo…ďe. Hara wooday waajitoray…óo …óum, o …ďooroo e keeferaaku makko?"
  54,52,"Kala huunde nden jeyaa…ďe …ďen huuwi, hino maandinaa ka nder …óeri Malaa'ika'en halfinaa…ďe …óum …ďen, …ďe winnday fow."
  54,53,"Kala ko fan…ói e kuugal maa haala, e ko mawni e mun, hino winndaa e …óeri golle …óin, maraa ka Alluwal reenaanagl. Aray nde …ďe yo…ďitoyee …óum."
  54,54,"Pellet, hulir…ďe Joomi mun siinu…ďe yamiraa…ói Makko wo…ó…óitoo e ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin, hino e Aljannaaji …ói …ďe neeminotoo e mun, can…ói ialy…ói."
  54,55,"E toolorde goonga, nde alaa haala meere wanaa bakkaatu, ka Laam…óo jogitii…óo kala huunde On, Hattan…óo Mo huunde ronkintaa. wota a lamda fii neemaaji ma…ď…ďe duumotoo…ói ton …óin."
